author: Howard Kurtz
title: When bad news is personal: Journalists, politicians fighting the virus
description: The thing about this virus is that it doesn’t care if you are a working stiff, a prince, or a movie star.
content:
For millions around the globe waking up Wednesday, the big news was that Prince Charles has the coronavirus.
